  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House",
    "asOf": "2021-09-03",
    "date": "2021-09-21T15:19:16Z",
    "text": "Taxpayer Penalty Protection Act of 2021\n\nThis bill exempts taxpayers from penalties for failure to pay estimated income tax in taxable years beginning in 2020 if such taxpayers (1) paid at least 70% of the tax due for the current year, and (2) paid 70% (90% if adjusted gross income exceeds $150,000) of tax shown on returns for the prior year."
  },
